message: 1、logo等图标样式优化，另外适配Android 12及以上版本桌面快捷方式图标||2、适配Android 11及以上版本锁屏和Tile快速访问电子钱包模拟卡片特性||3、修复bug
message_en: 1、Optimized the logo and other icon styles, and adapted to the desktop shortcut icons of Android 12 and above.||2、Adapt to Android 11 and above to quickly access the features of e-wallet simulation cards on the lock screen and Tile.||3、Known bug fixes.
